{"tid":1439022,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請積極將藍屍廢老非人化","createTime":"2019-08-10T03:26:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T08:20:56.000Z","uid":160176,"like":171,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":60,"replies":[{"pid":"c78e6fe4ade7ce8ac87cff83b9aecd057f803f4b","tid":1439022,"uid":160176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:26:54.000Z","msg":"支那的一國兩制工作室已經火力全開<br />\n<br />\n他們的文宣工作在近日亦進行得如火如荼<br />\n<br />\n其中一個愛用手段就是配合黑警賤畜，將示威者以「蟑螂」代稱<br />\n<br />\n並繪製卡通去加以形象化、非人化<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然我們早以「狗」代稱黑警匪類<br />\n<br />\n但對於那些助紂為虐的藍屍廢老，卻鮮少將他們非人化、形象化<br />\n<br />\n因此我推薦未來文宣用「藍蛆」稱呼撐狗藍屍廢老<br />\n<br />\n（藍屍一詞雖然可用，但這詞語沒有任何形象化空間，僅僅是黃屍的相反詞）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n藍蛆一詞，「藍」是指明那些廢老、廢中的政治立場<br />\n<br />\n「蛆」則是指明他們如同腐肉、糞便裡滋生的蛆蟲一樣<br />\n<br />\n他們盲目、骯髒，只能依附於惡臭腐敗的制度裡，噁心且令人厭惡<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8SCK2sH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8SCK2sH.jpg&h=94b53a03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6YO2O7J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6YO2O7J.jpg&h=27f8730c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s9cOKHJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs9cOKHJ.jpg&h=e26d153d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3LUYnup.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3LUYnup.jpg&h=db5f1093&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「藍蛆」一詞源於台灣，本來用來稱呼國民黨的支持者<br />\n<br />\n由於台灣的藍蛆和香港的藍屍都是愚蠢盲目的愛支病患者<br />\n<br />\n因此只需要稍加轉譯，即可以為我們的文宣所用<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在文宣上，我們可以效法親支那報紙，<br />\n<br />\n將藍蛆繪以卡通，多加評擊<br />\n<br />\n透過標籤那些廢老、廢中，積極貶損他們的自我形象"},{"pid":"4bd66d56a0d357b0e6e0caddad19290ad69b7165","tid":1439022,"uid":160176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:28:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"03fd3053dcb217e3459afcecd331168c87c4c3cc","tid":1439022,"uid":160176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:28:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"76c60ad1f88bc5ea300164ac496a5bd909efbbde","tid":1439022,"uid":27146,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:29:04.000Z","msg":"支蛆藍蛆是一對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3243ea22400ed97b6852e1195a04ce4e3abfa82","tid":1439022,"uid":261896,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:29:57.000Z","msg":"藍蛆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e105116e82b0e4dff0462a8ed369f511aa7d8f7c","tid":1439022,"uid":45660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:32:07.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b711aa7d9869a6cc80ce2ee9aa1d4fc1307ba6ee","tid":1439022,"uid":39796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:32:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9443f7d4812c6db35b86195616f0f7e5ee3f6b40","tid":1439022,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:33:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f1db5b364e37777b0857703b75ebfd6557819cd","tid":1439022,"uid":160176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:34:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"207cdb903e460ac64046183b51476d7c14a943d3","tid":1439022,"uid":160176,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:36:36.000Z","msg":"所有敵人的手法都要認真學習<br />\n加以運用"},{"pid":"0d0b8ba87011ffbeac8ccd456e684b94e8a520eb","tid":1439022,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:38:00.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"912f018e9ca01fcfcd82aedb83e18aec973ed879","tid":1439022,"uid":108016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:39:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=